  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to LAME</title>

    <para>
      The <application>LAME</application> package contains an MP3
      encoder and optionally, an MP3 frame analyzer. This is useful
      for creating and analyzing compressed audio files.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

